title: 'Best basic head set.'
body: 'This model is excellent. Why This one is perfect for making calls which is my primary purpose of purchase. Audibility is clear for both me and for the opposite end. The mic is adequately good. The ear piece design is comfortable and fits perfectly. No falling off. Easy to identify left and right ear piece. On few occasions I use to hear music and watch media files though I am not an expert in analysing music oriented criteria for me this is fine for hearing music too. Finally this is my 3rd purchase the previous two are still working fine for 8 plus months. Clearly I am satisfied.'
